{
  "type": "doc",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": { "level": 1 },
      "content": [
        { "type": "text", "text": "协作论文平台 / Collaboration Tool" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "italic" }], "text": "Abstract: " },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "We present a Phase 1 paper authoring platform that treats the document as a heterogeneous content graph rather than a flat token stream. Y.Doc (CRDT) holds the editable tree; Postgres holds the citation graph and provenance chain. The editor pairs human authors with AI agents — Citation Agent and Inline Editor Agent — under a capability-based access model. "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [{ "type": "italic" }],
          "text": "摘要："
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "本文介绍了 Phase 1 的协作论文平台原型，把文档建模为异构内容图：Y.Doc CRDT 承载可编辑树，Postgres 承载引用图与来源链。编辑器把人作者与 AI agent 放在同一权限模型里管理。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": { "level": 2 },
      "content": [
        { "type": "text", "text": "1. Introduction · 引言" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "We follow the foundation-models taxonomy from "
        },
        {
          "type": "citationRef",
          "attrs": {
            "blockId": "blk-cite-001",
            "citationId": "10.1145/3531146.3533104",
            "label": "Bommasani et al., 2022"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " and the Yjs CRDT design from "
        },
        {
          "type": "citationRef",
          "attrs": {
            "blockId": "blk-cite-002",
            "citationId": "10.48550/arXiv.2310.06770",
            "label": "Nicolaescu, 2023"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "。开放评审场景的可信度问题参照 "
        },
        {
          "type": "citationRef",
          "attrs": {
            "blockId": "blk-cite-003",
            "citationId": "10.1126/science.abe6396",
            "label": "Ross-Hellauer, 2024"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "。中文学术出版协作工具相关讨论可参 "
        },
        {
          "type": "citationRef",
          "attrs": {
            "blockId": "blk-cite-004",
            "citationId": "10.7717/peerj-cs.2024-zh",
            "label": "王 & Zhang, 2024"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The 损失函数 "
        },
        {
          "type": "inlineEquation",
          "attrs": {
            "blockId": "blk-ie-001",
            "latex": "\\mathcal{L} = -\\sum_i \\log p_\\theta(y_i \\mid x_i)"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is minimised over a reference dataset "
        },
        {
          "type": "datasetRef",
          "attrs": {
            "blockId": "blk-data-001",
            "citationId": "10.5281/zenodo.10000001",
            "label": "IPUMS 2024"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "equation",
      "attrs": {
        "blockId": "blk-eq-001",
        "latex": "\\rho(t) = \\frac{1}{Z(\\beta)} \\exp\\bigl(-\\beta H(t)\\bigr)"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": { "level": 2 },
      "content": [
        { "type": "text", "text": "2. Method · 方法" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "annotationAnchor",
              "attrs": { "anchorId": "anchor-method-001" }
            }
          ],
          "text": "We adopt a hybrid Yjs (CRDT) + Postgres model"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "：tree edits live in Y.Doc; citation, provenance, capability rows persist in Postgres. AI agents are first-class principals (kind='agent') and acquire capabilities through the same grant model as humans."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "computationalCell",
      "attrs": {
        "blockId": "blk-cc-001",
        "cellId": "cell-001",
        "kernel": "molab",
        "sourceCode": "import numpy as np\n\n# minimum reproducible example\ndef energy(t, beta=1.0):\n    return -np.log(np.exp(-beta * t).sum())\n\nprint(energy(np.linspace(0, 1, 100)))"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "We benchmark against the BibTeX-derived dataset described in "
        },
        {
          "type": "citationRef",
          "attrs": {
            "blockId": "blk-cite-005",
            "citationId": "10.1145/3531146.3533104",
            "label": "Bommasani et al., 2022"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "。Phase 1 D15 验收要求双语样张完整跑通 4 个导出格式（HTML / Word / JATS / PDF）。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "attrs": {
        "blockId": "blk-fig-001",
        "src": "/demo/figure-architecture.svg"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "figureCaption",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "图 1 / Figure 1: Phase 1 architecture — Y.Doc tree on the left, Postgres graph on the right, gateway capability shim in the middle."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": { "level": 2 },
      "content": [
        { "type": "text", "text": "3. Discussion · 讨论" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }],
          "text": "Trade-offs."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " 网关连接级鉴权简化了 Phase 1 的实现，但章节级隔离推迟到 Phase 3 子文档拆分。Provenance "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [{ "type": "italic" }],
          "text": "agentContext"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " 字段（modelId / promptHash / inputSkillIds / toolCalls[]）确保 AI 的每一次介入都可审计，符合系统提示词第一性原理 #11。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }],
          "text": "Limitations."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " Phase 1 不实施开放评审 / fork-merge UI / 客户端 BYO 模型 — these belong to Phase 3+. The two-author MVP path covered by this specimen is what Phase 1 commits to ship."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
